A modern **Skill Swap mobile application frontend** built using **React Native** on **Expo Snack**.  
This app allows users to exchange skills by connecting learners and mentors in a simple and interactive way.

---

## ğŸ“± Project Overview

The **Skill Swap App** is designed to help users:
- Share their skills
- Learn new skills from others
- Connect with people based on interests
- Swap skills instead of paying money

This repository contains **frontend-only implementation**.

